Gigi Rice https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gigi_Rice 0 Georgeanne Marie "Gigi" Rice is an American actress in movies and television shows. Rice graduated from the Ohio State University, with a bachelor of fine arts in musical theatre. Following her graduation, Rice served as an apprentice at Burt Reynolds's Maltz Jupiter Theatre, in Jupiter, Florida. While there, she appeared in Mame, directed by Charles Nelson Reilly, and I'm Not Rappaport, directed by Burt Reynolds.
